Spam Annihilator
Assignment #1

COMPILATION: This project can be added directly into Intellij and compiled! Just checkout the repository
using the built in project creation tool.

If not using Intellij use the following commands.

cd src/sample
javac *.java
cd ..
java sample.Main

USAGE: Upon starting the program, select a valid directory matching this structure:

/train/ham/ -> contains ham emails for training
/train/spam/
/test/ham/
/test/spam/

The classifier will then preform the classification and then output the relevant data.